lead_paragraph: Lock Courtney Lawes has been recalled to the England squad to play Ireland in the Six Nations at Twickenham on Saturday after Joe Launchbury was ruled out by a hamstring strain, the Rugby Football Union said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Lawes Returns to England Squad in Place of Launchbury
headline.main: Lawes Returns to England Squad in Place of Launchbury
